 ```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="dad54-141">No entanto, o seguinte construtor com os seguintes caracteres especiais escapado criará uma <xref:System.Net.Cookie> que podem ser adicionados a um <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instância:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dad54-141">However, the following constructor with these special characters escaped will create a <xref:System.Net.Cookie> that can be added to a <xref:System.Net.CookieContainer> instance:</span></span>  
 
 ```csharp
